		<title>Mayo Clinic experimental dual-drug nanotherapy crosses the blood-brain barrier and improved survival in preclinical glioblastoma models</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-experimental-dual-drug-nanotherapy-crosses-the-blood-brain-barrier-and-improved-survival-in-preclinical-glioblastoma-models/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[brittanycordeiro]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 13:01:21 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Cancer]]></category>
